<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Twenty-sixth session 
</b>Agenda item 3 
<b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Andorra,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote> Angola,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote> Armenia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote> Australia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote> Austria, Belgium,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote> Bolivia (Plurinational 
